ces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n個案例好恐怖:<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://legalref.judiciary.hk/lrs/common/search/search_result_detail_frame.jsp?DIS=98884&amp;QS=%28吳錫基%29&amp;TP=JU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flegalref.judiciary.hk%2Flrs%2Fcommon%2Fsearch%2Fsearch_result_detail_frame.jsp%3FDIS%3D98884%26QS%3D%2528%E5%90%B3%E9%8C%AB%E5%9F%BA%2529%26TP%3DJU&d=FTP9oA4bKBMrVBU8AKa4Kcn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=9c649030\" target=\"_blank\">http://legalref.judiciary.hk/lrs/common/search/search_result_detail_frame.jsp?DIS=98884&amp;QS=%28吳錫基%29&amp;TP=JU</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n56.  As previously mentioned, a final witness was called for the 1st applicant after his case had been closed.  This was Mr Cheung Yuk Keung who is a triad member serving a sentence of 25 years&rsquo; imprisonment for drug offences.  He wrote to the court because he believed he could give relevant evidence in respect of Li Cho Ming and his evidence was in fact interposed in the course of the judge&rsquo;s summing up.  He accused Li of being a hypocrite, not a genuine Christian and of being motivated solely by his desire to obtain a determinate sentence.  <strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">He also alleged that Li Cho Ming had said he would ask &ldquo;a rich man&rdquo; who was unnamed and unable to be identified by Mr Cheung for $2 million for each of the three immunity witnesses in order to settle their families. </span></strong> He said Li Cho Ming did not say what would happen if the money was not paid.  The thrust of his evidence was that Li Cho Ming was not a truthful person and had lied in court. <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n每人二百萬安家費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n安家費真係直譯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71e8fdd60f25045417eb35ab386080414b737f9f","tid":287694,"uid":2107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T00:31:37.000Z","msg":"又賣蝦片 又斬豬肉"},{"pid":"e74671c7f0c70512b6246799686661b924ce12eb","tid":287694,"uid":25825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T00:39:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88953ce76ce998096ca6bf38a8eabc676c3f51a2","tid":287694,"uid":65330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T00:50:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9228024cc1a14e64122adb6872626802c2cc335e","tid":287694,"uid":76143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T00:52:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1677556fec7f84bae3a078a3994b2fdbc27c2eba","tid":287694,"uid":44243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T01:14:43.000Z","msg":"實捉到你，講緊指使人去殺人個2位"},{"pid":"333c978154b1f0944679239281683506ca5e8732","tid":287694,"uid":39324,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T01:19:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6a05b68153f239322fbc8723bc869cdb1d8d9839","tid":287694,"uid":40903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T01:26:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2f209ada741e51d7db3165d16623910ea8d416b4","tid":287694,"uid":43119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T01:39:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"37c0145c4e159974a0613b24620f167c6b966913","tid":287694,"uid":93217,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T01:42:39.000Z","msg":"人在做，天在看<br />\n我信呢個世界有報應"},{"pid":"db3117ee90b1f797d34512db054b9c2f0b62f123","tid":287694,"uid":12021,"